ygData.subject: Fletching information
ygData.msgSnippet: As a fletcher I have been tracking the results of different combination of arrow components. As any fletcher knows though is that there are over one hundred
ygData.messageBody:
As a fletcher I have been tracking the results of different combination of
arrow components. As any fletcher knows though is that there are over one
hundred different combinations. So, I have posted an excel spreadsheet with
what I have and hope that some of you other fletchers will help complete the
information. Any little bit would be great. You will need to navigate
through the menu, asher stuff| pcgames, to find it.
http://www.whyweb.com/personal/dasher

Thanks
Rithannan of Cazic-Thule
